I found a more important functional gap than pure test config: account-scoped `SyncNode` never hydrates existing sessions from the server, and its Socket.IO handlers don’t parse `new-session` payload metadata into real `SessionInfo`. That would leave the app/daemon blind on cold start even though the unit tests are green. I’m fixing that path and tightening the boundary validation at the same time.
